Satyr: The Edtech Startup Namer

Innovation, disruption, revolution. It all starts with a name.

 
 

About

What is Satyr?

Satyr is an innovative tool that takes the pain out of naming your educational technology (or edtech) startup. We all know that education is ripe for disruption, but you'll never get your foot in the door without a compelling product or company name.

How does it work?

Satyr uses advanced algorithms to perform analysis of industry-leading brand names in the edtech space to generate a market-ready, competitively-viable product name for your startup.

How do I use it?

We've done all the heavy lifting for you. Simply click "generate" and Satyr will start the evaluation and generation process providing you with the best name for your startup. Of course we recommend you still do some A/B testing and market trials.

What does it cost?

Nothing!*
*While there's no up-front cost to using Satyr, your use of Satyr constitutes an agreement for exchange of a 1% private equity stake of your startup. Good luck getting a deal that great from a VC!
